title: The_Coral_Gables_Gazette
exrest: Coral Gables Gazette was an online newspaper based in Coral Gables, Florida covering Coral Gables, South Miami, Coconut Grove, Pinecrest and Brickell. The newspaper was owned by Limestone Communications, Inc. The paper was in publication from 2009 to 2012.
